{"tid":2009638,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]全世界男人都知道的「那個泳池」例のプール，拒絕片商入場拍攝的原因？","createTime":"2020-05-10T01:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T04:06:44.000Z","uid":297241,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a20d1cd60e2f920e680ae19df534fb2ba90d8e08","tid":2009638,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:43:14.000Z","msg":"全世界男人都知道的「那個泳池」例のプール，拒絕片商入場拍攝的原因？<br />\n<br />\n全世界男人都認識的「那個泳池」，可能是全世界知名度最高的泳池ＸＤ<br />\n<br />\n它位於新宿1丁目19-10的片場「Hanazono Room」，由管理公司「P studio」持有。<br />\n<br />\n有網民爆料，指泳池每次租給片商後，池內殘留大量男優及女優「做運動」後的體液，業主每次要<span style=\"color: red;\">把整個泳池的水放掉重注，又要進行大量消毒工作，在租金和維護成本之間難取得平衡</span>，而調整租金也不容易，故<span style=\"color: red;\">泳池現已拒絕小電影拍攝</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這項消息<span style=\"color: red;\">震驚許多網民</span>，紛紛標註「#例 の プール」發帖「哀號」<br />\n<br />\n但其實還是有不少寫真水着女星、私影會等會租用泳池，以「那個泳池」今時的知名度，應該還是不愁沒有客源的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.japhub.com/202005/ljTsHf81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F202005%2FljTsHf81.jpg&h=4fb128ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a32a851619f763bf5c1f7868aff7652ee5924a92","tid":2009638,"uid":189528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:47:45.000Z","msg":"童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3015050dbda8735bff309b67ca0080be45239e2","tid":2009638,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a32a851619f763bf5c1f7868aff7652ee5924a92","tid":2009638,"uid":189528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:47:45.000Z","msg":"童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T02:07:51.000Z","msg":"細蚊仔就睇av <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma